I sure do love these games!!
Great game. Google Story line

Just love these games the adventure the puzzles and solving the problems. Since discovering that it is much cheaper to buy the full game instead of buying coins +++ in the free game I have not looked back. This way it has saved me pounds.
Just have to say this, if possible please make another New York mystery. It's so good, though the puzzles were a bit of nuisance. However, I like a challenge
As usual New York Mysteries does not disappoint. Love this game.

I enjoyed the game. Has all the extras you look for in a game: hidden objects throughout, customizable difficulty setting, interactive map and bonus game! If wasn't SO PRICEY and more affordable like DOMINI GAMES, it'd be 5 star worthy!
The best in the series so far and I love them all... very entertaining and awesome story line for all four games. Worth the money.

The story and game play seemed rushed. It is difficult to tell if tapping on objects registers because of how slow the game reacts at times. The story didn't have much continuity. The main character seemed incompetent, which was frustrating because I never felt that in earlier games. The art and voice acting were wonderful. I appreciate the built in game guide.
Another great NYC mysteries game
Thoroughly enjoyed
Game will not open on my tablet.
Love this game! So many places to explore! Great bonus game as well!
Fun so far...
Great game thanks.
As always, excellent. Love the art work.
Not as intuitive as the other games. Wait for it to go on discount.

Another great game! Graphics good, storyline interesting, morphing objects and collectibles. Well done BN, so glad could purchase game and not use coins. I am looking forward to the next game as all your games are so good.
Amazing game with an interesting story. I really enjoyed this one everything about it was great.

The cut away scenes are detalied and lush. The story is intriquing. Most of all i love that 5BN lets you buy the game outright. Well done 5BN. Keep 'um coming please! btw $6.99 is a bargain for how wonderful this whole game is.
Awesome! 5BN Games make gaming fun, exciting, and exceptional. Unique storyline, interesting characters, beautiful graphics and design.
Thanks for the full version, love it!
